WEBVTT

25:41.760 --> 25:43.560 line:80%
Why would the authorities lie?

25:44.510 --> 25:47.880 line:80%
Just as your uncle
colluded with Advisor Guo when he tried to

25:47.900 --> 25:49.590 line:80%
seize your family's property—

25:49.590 --> 25:50.910 line:80%
even a small county office

25:50.910 --> 25:52.390 line:80%
is full of intrigue.
